entries.femaleVariant: Just shut your fuckin' mouth an' listen for once!
No, you shut up! You don't know shit, old man. How many people got zeroed 'cause of them?!
More like how many survived, you gutless little gonk! And that's the truth!
Fine, gimme the truth, Gen Zero. Let's hear it!
All right, you ungrateful little shit! If it weren't for the 'Tinos, you'd be stuck pissing yourself in your pad! They cleaned this place up!
Ah, don't give me that scop! Cops took care of things just fine before, plus we didn't have to pay 'em! Shit was normal!
Oh, I fucking swear. The police?! Didn't even step foot here! This was practically a combat zone! But the Tinos came in, brought order. That's the goddamn truth.
Y'know what? Fuck you and your fuckin' 'Tinos!
